reviewText: If Telly Savalas' character were consistent he would have killed Mark Lester's character early on in the movie, however, then you would not have had a movie. It is neither Telly Savalas's nor Mark Lester's best work, but overall the movie is OK. Just don't expect too much, and enjoy it for what it is.
MARK LESTER, THE YOUNG STAR OF " OLIVER ", IN A SPETACULAR THRILLER, WITH TELLY SAVALLAS AND FRANCO NERO.
